Notes. This species is known only from one, partly damaged, specimen (male). The structure of antennal flagellum, distal segment of the maxillary palpi, pro-, mesotarsi and hind legs is unknown. Distribution. This species has been collected in the following ecoregion of East Africa ( Somalia ): Hobyo grasslands and shrublands (
Fig. 46
).

